### Brackets Git Plug-in
* Allows Git operations within the text editor
* Install using File menu, Extension Manager
* Available, Search for "Brackets Git"
* Use Git icon in upper right


### Code Demo - Page Template
* Pull demo code from Mark-Seaman/UNC-BACS350-Demo repo
* See full demo at [Demo 32](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs350/demo/32)
* View code in Brackets


### Demo 32 Features
* Secret settings design pattern (db.php)
* Simplified logging (log.php)
* Templates for views (note.html, add.html, edit.html)
* Button toolbar (index.php)
* Simplified controller (note.php)


### Simplified controller
* Visit code for note.php
* Model - Data CRUD operations
* Views - User experience
* Controller - Business logic for app


### Controller Design
* When page is loaded "action" is passed in
* CRUD actions
    * create
    * read
    * update
    * delete
* View actions
    * add
    * list
    * edit
    * remove


### CRUD actions
* Parse off the input parameters
* Use POST or GET method to pass arguments
* If info is present then do the action
* Pass true if successful
* Go to next page on success


### View actions
* Present the appropriate HTML 
* Return HTML from each action
* Populate views with data
* Show the form


